Package com.example.trialio.controllers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChangeUsernameCommand.OnResultListener
    Interface which represent the receiver for the invoker when the command finished execution
    CurrentUserHandler.OnUserFetchCallback
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a User object is fetched.
    ExperimentManager.OnExperimentFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when an Experiment document is fetched from the database.
    ExperimentManager.OnManyExperimentsFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a collection of Experiments is fetched from the database.
    QuestionForumManager.OnManyQuestionsFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a collection of Questions is fetched from the database.
    QuestionForumManager.OnManyRepliesFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a collection of Questions is fetched from the database.
    QuestionForumManager.OnQuestionFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when an Question document is fetched from the database.
    QuestionForumManager.OnReplyFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a Reply document is fetched from the database.
    TrialManager.OnAllVisibleTrialsFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when all visible trials of a collection have been fetched.
    UserManager.OnManyUsersFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a multiple User documents have been fetched from the Firestore database.
    UserManager.OnUserFetchListener
    This interface represents an action to be taken when a User document is fetched from the Firestore database.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BarcodeManager  
    ChangeUsernameCommand
    This class follows the Command design pattern and represents the tasks to be performed to change the username of a given user in the system.
    CurrentUserHandler
    CurrentUserHandler handles accesses to the current user for an app instance.
    ExperimentManager
    ExperimentManager manages Experiments and is responsible for the persistence of Experiment data.
    QRCodeGenerator
    QRCodeGenerator generates QR code for trials when called
    QuestionForumManager
    QuestionForumManager manages Question and Reply Posts for an experiment and is responsible for the persistence of Post data.
    TrialManager
    TrialManager manages Trials for an experiment and is responsible for the persistence of Trial data.
    UserManager
    UserManager manages Users in the system and is responsible for the persistence of User data.
